Class JobTracker

java.lang.Object
  cmu.ds.mr.mapred.JobTracker

public class JobTracker
extends java.lang.Object

JobTracker is used to control all TaskTrackers All jobs are submitted to jobtracker and then assigned to all other tasktrackers
